name: these 7000 oaks do not exist
description: The strap is a reference to Joseph Beuys' "7000 oaks", but mixed with "This Cat Does Not Exist.com". In a way, it askes that after the AI used to generate the 7000 Oaks and minting an NFT, are the oaks here now? Celebraing the 100th year of Joseph Beuys.
